STATE of North Carolina
v.
Paul Michael BRANKS. No. 344P07. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 11, 2007. Emily H. Davis, Assistant Appellate Defender, for Branks. Hilda Burnett-Baker, Assistant Attorney General, Michael Bonfoey, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 20th day of July 2007 by Defendant in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 11th day of October 2007."
